projectDesc: Impedia is an appeal management system that enables proper communication of issues or appeals between students and authorities for IIITA.
CalIIITA is a scheduling app that keeps track of all the events that happen in IIITA and helps you manage your time effectively!
PuzzleDash is a remake of Chess Puzzle Rush, where you are challenged to solve a series of chess puzzles with increasing difficulty in limited time.
dankCLI is a CLI Image Captioning Tool or Meme Generator which automatically adds whitespace and text to top of your image through a CLI.
A web app that features a live map which visualizes the spread of Corona Virus (COVID-19) in Indian states so you can get a better overview of the spread.
Notes Keeper is an authenticated Notes WebApp(like Google Docs) built in Django with a WYSIWYG editor and optional public notes.
